<taxonomicName id="9BF55894F33F7C55CC8DCF03542CF35B" class="Amphibia" family="Pelobatidae" genus="Pelobates" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pelobates" order="Anura" pageId="17" pageNumber="148" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pelobates</taxonomicName>
, we hereby provide a key to summarize the main discriminating features within this group. Because several taxa are cryptic and lack diagnostic phenotypic differences, geographic origin remains an essential information.
</paragraph>
